{"tid":260750,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點解The Chainsmokers紅遍全球，農夫就仲係做緊二打六？","createTime":"2017-05-28T01:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T13:51:45.000Z","uid":35370,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f25433e26cc6880df5fe2964ec4213362d66cf2","tid":260750,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/9df0008e6fb01059154\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F9df0008e6fb01059154&h=fb97275e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得農夫仲高質喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔靠洗腦電音<br />\n歌好聽，詞又有意思<br />\n唔講要紅遍全球，點解農夫唔可以紅遍香港？<br />\n反而近年唱陳腔濫調嘅情歌K歌就街知巷聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到啲人識農夫係因為做二打六角色，或者做綜藝主持<br />\n而唔係因為識佢哋嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偉大航道真係好好聽又有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uglNXwhc_u0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuglNXwhc_u0&d=weW6yIUZoGcZx37EmzOfSm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8ddea6e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uglNXwhc_u0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認為農夫值得更紅嘅請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8284254424080bd4ed68b9d51ca74ac67d7592d5","tid":260750,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"123齊話聲"},{"pid":"340a9f4c9ac193bf01b6cf9b4b60221708d05eb2","tid":260750,"uid":41797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"當年中學聽學海無涯覺得好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家聽返就覺得原來中學生活已經唔再熟於我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b35f3b95497f1d267babe36e722127d3a26c2e","tid":260750,"uid":41797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年中學聽學海無涯覺得好貼切<img